### 2ï¸âƒ£ Fast Updates (Very Important)

React uses something called **Virtual DOM**.

Simple meaning:

ğŸ‘‰ When something changes, React updates only that part of the page
ğŸ‘‰ Not the full page reload

That makes apps:

* Faster
* Smooth
* Modern feeling

---

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Easy to Manage Big Applications

For example:

* Your CMARF project frontend
* Your Food ordering app
* Admin dashboard

If you use normal HTML + JS, it becomes messy in big projects.

React helps to:

